WEBVTT

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:43.520
Mr. Jiang Nanshuo,

00:00:43.960 --> 00:00:44.679
may I ask about the recent

00:00:44.679 --> 00:00:45.799
accusations that you abused a female college student

00:00:45.799 --> 00:00:46.920
and caused her death?

00:00:46.920 --> 00:00:47.320
Is it true?

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:47.920
Recently,

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:49.280
there have been many

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:50.479
false rumors about Liheng Group online.

00:00:51.240 --> 00:00:51.880
Regarding this,

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:53.960
I urge everyone not to spread or believe rumors.

00:00:54.359 --> 00:00:55.320
We at Liheng Group

00:00:55.439 --> 00:00:56.840
will continue to focus our energy

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:58.880
on matters beneficial to society.

00:00:59.079 --> 00:01:00.359
Today, we are holding this

00:01:00.359 --> 00:01:02.200
Artistic Nine-ball Charity Exhibition Match.

00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:04.599
All donations will go to charity organizations.

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:12.120
Well done.

00:01:12.680 --> 00:01:13.719
Using the guise of charity

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:15.599
to suppress public opinion against me.

00:01:20.799 --> 00:01:21.760
Why is she here?

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:26.319
To maximize the impact,

00:01:26.519 --> 00:01:28.439
I opened registration for this stream to the public.

00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:30.400
Anyone could sign up to participate.

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:31.519
It was my oversight.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:36.200
An oversight?

00:01:38.079 --> 00:01:38.640
Then,

00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:40.920
find a reason to escort her out.

00:01:48.719 --> 00:01:49.239
No need.

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:51.599
Let's just play along.

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:54.159
Let her use the gimmick of being the Chaoli Group heiress

00:01:54.480 --> 00:01:55.439
to bring me a new wave of

00:01:55.439 --> 00:01:56.599
traffic and wealth.

00:02:08.159 --> 00:02:09.319
After some spectacular performances,

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:11.520
the most popular player of this match

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:11.919
is...

00:02:12.240 --> 00:02:13.599
Nine-ball streamer Lin Lu!

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:18.400
Congratulations.

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:24.199
I also want to announce

00:02:24.639 --> 00:02:25.759
that at the next Chaoli Cup

00:02:25.759 --> 00:02:27.240
World Youth Championship,

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:28.800
I will participate as a player

00:02:29.439 --> 00:02:30.280
and challenge Hei Ba one-on-one.

00:02:31.960 --> 00:02:32.680
Missy,

00:02:33.599 --> 00:02:34.879
I am the best partner

00:02:35.240 --> 00:02:37.120
for Chaoli Group and the Billiards Association.

00:02:37.719 --> 00:02:38.919
Hei Ba simply cannot

00:02:38.919 --> 00:02:40.439
bring you any benefits.

00:02:41.639 --> 00:02:42.560
Regardless,

00:02:43.319 --> 00:02:44.719
Hei Ba has proven his strength

00:02:44.719 --> 00:02:45.919
on the playing field.

00:02:46.599 --> 00:02:47.319
What makes you think

00:02:48.120 --> 00:02:50.400
you can be a partner of my Chaoli Group?

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:52.199
Because you can hand out trophies?

00:02:54.439 --> 00:02:55.800
What exactly do you want?

00:02:57.159 --> 00:02:58.439
We at Chaoli Group

00:02:58.439 --> 00:03:00.400
do not need to partner with trash.

00:03:01.319 --> 00:03:03.599
If you want to be a partner of Chaoli Group,

00:03:03.879 --> 00:03:04.439
at the very least,

00:03:05.599 --> 00:03:07.199
you should prove you can play billiards.

00:03:07.599 --> 00:03:08.159
Fine.

00:03:08.639 --> 00:03:09.840
Since Missy Lin

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:12.080
is so eager to see my skills,

00:03:12.280 --> 00:03:14.159
I will invite Hei Ba right now

00:03:14.639 --> 00:03:15.919
to prove it to you.

00:03:15.960 --> 00:03:17.039
No need for Hei Ba to step in.

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:19.680
I can take you down myself.

00:03:21.960 --> 00:03:22.919
Jiang Nanshuo,

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:27.360
don't tell me

00:03:28.439 --> 00:03:29.879
you're afraid?

00:03:38.479 --> 00:03:40.319
I want to cooperate properly with Chaoli Group,

00:03:40.520 --> 00:03:42.039
but with Missy Lin's attitude,

00:03:43.039 --> 00:03:43.719
I have no choice but to

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:45.199
give up on this hope.

00:03:47.159 --> 00:03:48.319
Good that you know.

00:03:48.599 --> 00:03:49.840
Since Missy Lin

00:03:50.280 --> 00:03:51.560
humiliates me like this,

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:53.039
then naturally, I

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:54.199
cannot let

00:03:54.199 --> 00:03:55.080
Missy Lin off the hook either.

00:03:56.199 --> 00:03:57.000
What do you want to do?

00:03:58.120 --> 00:03:59.120
You made me lose face,

00:03:59.639 --> 00:04:00.599
so I have no choice but

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:02.919
to ruin your reputation as well.

00:04:05.800 --> 00:04:06.479
Let's break.

00:04:24.319 --> 00:04:24.920
Break.

00:04:33.519 --> 00:04:34.680
I heard Miss Lin

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:35.920
is a fan of Hei Ba.

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:37.519
Since ten years ago.

00:04:38.279 --> 00:04:39.480
What's that word again?

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:42.199
Sasaeng fan.

00:04:46.439 --> 00:04:47.759
I am a fan of Hei Ba.

00:04:50.319 --> 00:04:51.480
So, the dignified

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:53.279
Missy of the Chaoli Group,

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:55.240
daughter of the Billiards Association chairman,

00:04:55.439 --> 00:04:56.600
actually has the audacity to

00:04:56.879 --> 00:04:58.040
stand up for Hei Ba,

00:04:58.399 --> 00:04:59.399
throwing yourself at him.

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:00.720
Is there perhaps

00:05:01.360 --> 00:05:02.680
something fishy going on here?

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:05.720
Hei Ba wins with his skills.

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:07.839
A dog's eyes

00:05:07.920 --> 00:05:09.639
can only see filth.

00:05:11.839 --> 00:05:13.000
You think everyone is like you,

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.160
liking to play dirty tricks?

00:05:16.839 --> 00:05:19.000
My Lulu is actually a runaway princess!

00:05:19.600 --> 00:05:22.519
Reborn as a Tycoon's Daughter in the Billiards World.

00:05:23.399 --> 00:05:25.680
But you used to livestream racy content

00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:27.920
to seduce bosses into placing orders

00:05:28.079 --> 00:05:29.439
for paid companionship for games and chat.

00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:31.720
And one of those bosses

00:05:32.199 --> 00:05:33.079
was surnamed Lu.

00:05:34.199 --> 00:05:34.959
Miss Lin,

00:05:35.439 --> 00:05:36.560
you can't deny that, right?

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:43.279
I will crush you under my foot

00:05:43.560 --> 00:05:45.560
and see what waves you can make then.

00:05:46.839 --> 00:05:47.439
Of course,

00:05:48.040 --> 00:05:49.040
it doesn't matter if you don't remember.

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:50.240
After all,

00:05:50.279 --> 00:05:52.040
you also once snuck into my company

00:05:52.279 --> 00:05:53.120
to work as a training partner.

00:05:54.319 --> 00:05:55.160
You haven't forgotten, have you?

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:57.240
You call yourself the 9-Ball Queen,

00:05:57.399 --> 00:05:58.959
yet you oppose me time and again,

00:05:59.360 --> 00:06:01.240
even going so far as to ruin a charity event

00:06:01.399 --> 00:06:02.759
and turning everything upside down.

00:06:03.199 --> 00:06:03.879
While I, Jiang Nanshuo,

00:06:03.879 --> 00:06:05.720
and everything Liheng Group does

00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:07.720
is for the development of this industry.

00:06:08.079 --> 00:06:08.800
The charity match,

00:06:09.319 --> 00:06:10.120
I ask everyone

00:06:10.720 --> 00:06:11.680
to please support it.

00:06:11.680 --> 00:06:13.079
The dignified Miss Lin,

00:06:13.079 --> 00:06:14.639
to clear the name of a cancelled idol,

00:06:14.639 --> 00:06:15.800
actually did such a thing.

00:06:41.240 --> 00:06:42.319
You chose to be a dog,

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:44.319
threatening female streamers with secret recordings.

00:06:45.399 --> 00:06:46.680
But I chose to be a human.

00:06:47.040 --> 00:06:48.279
When a human gets bitten by a dog,

00:06:48.959 --> 00:06:50.199
they don't bite back.

00:06:50.639 --> 00:06:52.240
They just go get a rabies vaccine.

00:06:55.839 --> 00:06:56.480
Abuse,

00:06:57.160 --> 00:06:57.839
insults,

00:06:58.240 --> 00:06:58.920
doubts,

00:06:59.439 --> 00:07:00.240
slander.

00:07:01.319 --> 00:07:02.079
From the very first day I gave up

00:07:02.079 --> 00:07:03.560
the identity of Missy Li Yi

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:06.319
to become the nine-ball streamer Lin Lu,

00:07:06.680 --> 00:07:08.240
they have been pervasive.

00:07:09.079 --> 00:07:10.040
But so what?

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:12.240
I'm not going to admit defeat anyway.

00:07:44.879 --> 00:07:45.920
In the end,

00:07:46.279 --> 00:07:47.000
those things,

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:48.480
you did them all anyway.

00:07:48.600 --> 00:07:49.199
That's right.

00:07:50.399 --> 00:07:52.279
If I hadn't snuck into your company,

00:07:52.519 --> 00:07:53.360
how would I know

00:07:54.079 --> 00:07:55.519
that on that luxury yacht,

00:07:56.120 --> 00:07:57.360
there were so many of your escorts?

00:07:59.560 --> 00:08:01.319
It's that yacht of yours,

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:04.360
the one that was just seized recently.

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:07.079
You couldn't have forgotten, right?

00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:08.680
No.

00:08:09.519 --> 00:08:10.240
Don't worry.

00:08:10.920 --> 00:08:11.839
In the past,

00:08:12.360 --> 00:08:14.279
I was always the one cheering for you off-stage.

00:08:14.839 --> 00:08:16.040
This time, it's your turn.

00:08:16.959 --> 00:08:17.639
What you lost,

00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:19.920
I'll help you take it all back.

00:08:22.600 --> 00:08:23.600
That's still not okay.

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:25.120
It's not worth it.

00:08:25.600 --> 00:08:26.759
Why isn't it worth it?

00:08:28.879 --> 00:08:29.839
It's not just for you,

00:08:31.279 --> 00:08:32.000
but also for

00:08:32.639 --> 00:08:34.120
those girls who were hurt.

00:08:35.480 --> 00:08:36.240
It is worth it.

00:08:37.240 --> 00:08:38.799
Besides, that Jiang Nanshuo

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:40.879
shook off all the dirty work so cleanly.

00:08:41.879 --> 00:08:42.519
Only if

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:45.480
I speak out about how I put myself in the trap

00:08:45.519 --> 00:08:46.559
will it be convincing.

00:08:48.600 --> 00:08:49.840
It can also buy Sister Yixin

00:08:50.080 --> 00:08:51.240
some time.

00:08:53.039 --> 00:08:53.879
Besides,

00:08:55.639 --> 00:08:57.080
I have a clear conscience.

00:08:59.960 --> 00:09:00.799
What are you talking about?

00:09:00.919 --> 00:09:01.720
What yacht?

00:09:02.840 --> 00:09:03.440
I don't understand.

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:04.960
Playing dumb?

00:09:05.879 --> 00:09:07.240
Then you can sue me for defamation.

00:09:07.639 --> 00:09:08.480
Anyway,

00:09:09.559 --> 00:09:11.840
I've already said it in front of everyone.

00:09:12.039 --> 00:09:14.120
If you still want to prove your innocence,

00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:16.240
just holding a charity match

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:18.240
probably won't be enough.

00:09:18.639 --> 00:09:19.000
You...

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:21.679
Hit me if you have the guts!

00:09:27.080 --> 00:09:28.279
Cut the livestream!

00:09:28.679 --> 00:09:29.320
Understood.

00:10:04.879 --> 00:10:06.519
I've finally found the last straw

00:10:06.519 --> 00:10:07.679
that will break you.

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:11.799
I didn't expect Hei Ba to get involved.

00:10:12.320 --> 00:10:13.759
He's really risking it all.

00:10:14.399 --> 00:10:15.399
It has nothing to do with Hei Ba.

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:17.679
It was my own choice.

00:10:18.679 --> 00:10:19.399
Jiang Nanshuo.

00:10:19.960 --> 00:10:21.879
You are nothing but a complete...

00:10:21.879 --> 00:10:22.639
pervert.

00:10:22.879 --> 00:10:23.679
Scum.

00:10:24.559 --> 00:10:25.279
Everything you've done...

00:10:25.279 --> 00:10:26.200
will bring you retribution.

00:10:27.039 --> 00:10:28.080
What did I do?

00:10:28.679 --> 00:10:29.480
I simply gave...

00:10:29.559 --> 00:10:31.320
all the girls who wanted to make money...

00:10:31.919 --> 00:10:32.639
a home.

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:34.200
Gave them a shortcut...

00:10:34.759 --> 00:10:36.240
to a life of wealth and luxury.

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:39.080
They made the choice themselves.

00:10:39.639 --> 00:10:40.960
It has nothing to do with me.

00:10:41.720 --> 00:10:42.759
Bullshit!

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:45.840
They were just looking for a job.

00:10:46.559 --> 00:10:48.000
But you treated them like products...

00:10:48.360 --> 00:10:49.600
to be sold off cheap.

00:10:51.879 --> 00:10:52.919
No decent person...

00:10:52.919 --> 00:10:54.240
comes here looking for a job.

00:10:54.960 --> 00:10:55.759
I just helped them...

00:10:55.759 --> 00:10:57.440
achieve their dreams.

00:10:58.480 --> 00:10:59.600
You're a lunatic.

00:11:00.960 --> 00:11:01.519
That's right.

00:11:02.360 --> 00:11:03.600
I am a lunatic.

00:11:05.039 --> 00:11:05.759
Are you scared?

00:11:09.519 --> 00:11:11.080
How dare you still question me?

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:11.879
Fine.

00:11:12.600 --> 00:11:13.759
I'll tell you another secret.

00:11:15.799 --> 00:11:16.960
Whether on the yacht...

00:11:17.279 --> 00:11:18.279
or in the livestream rooms...

00:11:18.679 --> 00:11:19.559
all the mirrors...

00:11:19.919 --> 00:11:20.919
are one-way mirrors.

00:11:21.279 --> 00:11:22.159
Everything...

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:23.440
I've recorded it all.

00:11:24.159 --> 00:11:25.639
You want us to go down together?

00:11:26.600 --> 00:11:28.279
Then I'll take all that footage...

00:11:28.519 --> 00:11:29.600
and put it online.

00:11:30.919 --> 00:11:31.879
But don't worry.

00:11:32.759 --> 00:11:33.600
I know...

00:11:34.159 --> 00:11:35.320
you didn't do anything.

00:11:35.799 --> 00:11:37.320
But I'll edit it to look like...

00:11:38.960 --> 00:11:40.120
you did everything.

00:11:42.840 --> 00:11:44.519
And those streamers I signed...

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:46.399
are nothing but my merchandise.

00:11:47.080 --> 00:11:48.480
All the billiards matches here...

00:11:48.679 --> 00:11:49.879
have backers behind them.

00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:51.320
As long as the spectators...

00:11:51.320 --> 00:11:52.639
are willing to pay the price...

00:11:54.159 --> 00:11:55.879
they can have any woman they want.

00:12:03.720 --> 00:12:04.320
Oh, right.

00:12:05.679 --> 00:12:07.000
Let me tell you one more thing.

00:12:07.720 --> 00:12:08.600
Your idol...

00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:10.200
Ten years ago...

00:12:10.799 --> 00:12:12.200
I was the one who made Lang Jiu...

00:12:13.120 --> 00:12:14.639
commit perjury to frame him.

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:16.480
Getting him banned for ten years.

00:12:17.120 --> 00:12:18.200
As for his woman...

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:19.720
I slept with her too.

00:12:19.919 --> 00:12:20.600
And now...

00:12:21.519 --> 00:12:22.039
You...

00:12:22.679 --> 00:12:24.080
and the Chaoli Group...

00:12:25.200 --> 00:12:26.320
will all be mine.

00:12:26.720 --> 00:12:27.360
So?

00:12:28.039 --> 00:12:29.200
What can you do to me?

00:12:30.440 --> 00:12:31.799
We can't do anything to you.

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:39.320
But the law can.